Fish Fillets - Next Generation
http://fillets.sf.net
------------------------------

Compile requirements:
- (autoconf, automake) OR aap
- pkg-config


Library SDL = Simple DirectMedia Layer (video, input, sound)
- libSDL >= 1.2, www.libsdl.org

Library SDL_mixer (multiple sounds)
- libSDL_mixer, http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_mixer/

Library SDL_image (png, jpg support)
- libSDL_image, http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_image/

Library LUA (script language, used for debug console, configuration, levels,...)
- liblua50, www.lua.org
- liblualib50

Library Boost - http://www.boost.org/
- libboost_filesystem (portable filesystem paths)

//-----------------------------------------------------------------
How to run:
1. Compile (./configure && make) OR (app)
2. Download data from http://sf.net/projects/fillets
3. cp src/game/fillets path_to_data
4. cd path_to_data
5. ./fillets

Alternative you can copy all game data to $HOME/fillets-ng

Controls:
small fish ... arrows
big fish ... keypad (4568)

